        <p style="font-size:0.9rem;color:#6B7280;line-height:1.75;margin-bottom:1.25rem;">Everything we build is filtered through a Christ-centered worldview. We don't leave our values at the door &mdash; they're the foundation of every decision we make, from product formulation to how we treat customers.</p>
        <ul style="list-style:none;display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:0.5rem;">
          <li style="font-size:0.8125rem;color:#6B7280;display:flex;align-items:center;gap:8px;"><span style="color:#06A5C5;font-size:0.625rem;">&#9679;</span>Purpose over profit</li>
          <li style="font-size:0.8125rem;color:#6B7280;display:flex;align-items:center;gap:8px;"><span style="color:#06A5C5;font-size:0.625rem;">&#9679;</span>Character in every interaction</li>
          <li style="font-size:0.8125rem;color:#6B7280;display:flex;align-items:center;gap:8px;"><span style="color:#06A5C5;font-size:0.625rem;">&#9679;</span>Integrity above all</li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <!-- Performance-First -->
      <div class="values-card">
        <div style="display:inline-flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;width:56px;height:56px;border-radius:12px;background:linear-gradient(135deg,rgba(239,68,68,0.1),rgba(239,68,68,0.04));border:1px solid rgba(239,68,68,0.2);margin-bottom:1.25rem;">
          <svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#EF4444" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" aria-hidden="true"><polyline points="22 12 18 12 15 21 9 3 6 12 2 12"/></svg>
        </div>
        <h3 style="font-family:Georgia,serif;font-size:1.25rem;font-weight:700;letter-spacing:-0.01em;color:#0D0D0D;margin-bottom:0.75rem;">Performance-First</h3>
        <p style="font-size:0.9rem;color:#6B7280;line-height:1.75;margin-bottom:1.25rem;">We hold ourselves to elite standards. Mediocrity is not an option. Whether you're writing copy, formulating a product, or answering a support ticket, we expect the kind of output that makes people say "this is different."</p>
        <ul style="list-style:none;display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:0.5rem;">
          <li style="font-size:0.8125rem;color:#6B7280;display:flex;align-items:center;gap:8px;"><span style="color:#EF4444;font-size:0.625rem;">&#9679;</span>Results over activity</li>
          <li style="font-size:0.8125rem;color:#6B7280;display:flex;align-items:center;gap:8px;"><span style="color:#EF4444;font-size:0.625rem;">&#9679;</span>High standards, always</li>
          <li style="font-size:0.8125rem;color:#6B7280;display:flex;align-items:center;gap:8px;"><span style="color:#EF4444;font-size:0.625rem;">&#9679;</span>Own your outcomes</li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <!-- Community -->
      <div class="values-card">
        <div style="display:inline-flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;width:56px;height:56px;border-radius:12px;background:linear-gradient(135deg,rgba(34,197,94,0.1),rgba(34,197,94,0.04));border:1px solid rgba(34,197,94,0.2);margin-bottom:1.25rem;">
          <svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#22C55E" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M17 21v-2a4 4 0 0 0-4-4H5a4 4 0 0 0-4 4v2"/><circle cx="9" cy="7" r="4"/><path d="M23 21v-2a4 4 0 0 0-3-3.87"/><path d="M16 3.13a4 4 0 0 1 0 7.75"/></svg>
        </div>
        <h3 style="font-family:Georgia,serif;font-size:1.25rem;font-weight:700;letter-spacing:-0.01em;color:#0D0D0D;margin-bottom:0.75rem;">Community</h3>
        <p style="font-size:0.9rem;color:#6B7280;line-height:1.75;margin-bottom:1.25rem;">We're building something together &mdash; teammates, not employees. Our best work comes from real relationships, honest feedback, and a shared commitment to the athletes we serve. We celebrate wins together and solve problems together.</p>
        <ul style="list-style:none;display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:0.5rem;">
          <li style="font-size:0.8125rem;color:#6B7280;display:flex;align-items:center;gap:8px;"><span style="color:#22C55E;font-size:0.625rem;">&#9679;</span>Teammates, not just coworkers</li>
          <li style="font-size:0.8125rem;color:#6B7280;display:flex;align-items:center;gap:8px;"><span style="color:#22C55E;font-size:0.625rem;">&#9679;</span>Radical transparency</li>
          <li style="font-size:0.8125rem;color:#6B7280;display:flex;align-items:center;gap:8px;"><span style="color:#22C55E;font-size:0.625rem;">&#9679;</span>Shared mission, shared wins</li>
        </ul>
      </div>

    </div>
  </div>
</section>

